{"tid":1263362,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔天橋伯伯 : 林鄭月娥請下台","createTime":"2019-06-28T06:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T22:40:43.000Z","uid":240973,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"deeaa988c0d8f34f805b5c942436760663489504","tid":1263362,"uid":240973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"今朝返工係天橋見到有個人掛住個牌係身派傳單，<br />\n未訓醒淨係見到狗官以為係反送中啲文宣就順手拎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onO4vEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonO4vEA.jpg&h=2bc33812&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上完去睇發現唔係，有無人都見過個伯伯或者知咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://waikuenleung.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/20180731_105416-e1541968235340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwaikuenleung.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F20180731_105416-e1541968235340.jpg&h=ba617ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPOSTED ONJUNE 15, 2019<br />\n林鄭月娥請下台<br />\n<br />\n香港不需要一個讀書年年考試第一的特首<br />\n香港需要的是一個懂得解決問題的特首<br />\n考試第一祗顯示她懂得應付考試<br />\n並不顯示她懂得如何解決問題<br />\n<br />\n從林鄭月娥上任後的表現可以看出解決問題肯定不是她的强項<br />\n大問題如樓價/土地問題及最近台灣疑犯引渡問題<br />\n小問題如找出我向廉署投訴袁國强及盧偉聰的進度問題<br />\n她都無法解決<br />\n<br />\n不要告訴我有40多年政府工作經驗是優點<br />\n她每天上班乘政府專車<br />\n衣食住行皆受照顧<br />\n生活跟社會完全脫節<br />\n不知民間疾苦<br />\n她肯定不適宜當香港特首<br />\n<br />\n根據她的强項 &ndash; 懂得應付考試<br />\n她最適合當教師<br />\n指導後輩如何應付考試<br />\n為香港及為她自已她應立即辭職轉職為教師<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://waikuenleung.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwaikuenleung.com%2F&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=22a332a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://waikuenleung.com/</a>"},{"pid":"b250dc2af89d35cd3adfe1597f74d206642b712c","tid":1263362,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0245f3c981775122384457edffa5dcb0d62adf0b","tid":1263362,"uid":143260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝伯伯身體健康"},{"pid":"98780cbeb8db8c71952a8ca6a3aa16d404c7cf25","tid":1263362,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f35285c7374d9e3ffc8ed39c78579d7faa1cbc2","tid":1263362,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"祝一世平安<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享"},{"pid":"886c8c3c987a4d27edd9b24d86b2b8221ac1eede","tid":1263362,"uid":58630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:47:53.000Z","msg":"呢個阿伯好似日日都係灣仔天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ab4320379145796ebaabcafeb6249fea37191c","tid":1263362,"uid":240973,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886c8c3c987a4d27edd9b24d86b2b8221ac1eede","tid":1263362,"uid":58630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:47:53.000Z","msg":"呢個阿伯好似日日都係灣仔天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無留意"},{"pid":"64f470fd1b937ea846775714ff6693944d7eabb7","tid":1263362,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:37:56.000Z","msg":"希望各位見到伯伯 可以過去同佢打下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c91c81a954d3ad63f68e0eb323c9605d5c83da3","tid":1263362,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64f470fd1b937ea846775714ff6693944d7eabb7","tid":1263362,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:37:56.000Z","msg":"希望各位見到伯伯 可以過去同佢打下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:59:23.000Z","msg":"真 肯行出黎真心唔易"},{"pid":"092a85c216bc141c6c8746a580415f4df2794966","tid":1263362,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:21:15.000Z","msg":"長命百歲"},{"pid":"5718321408e5725040dfe6a2f03c69282e3b565a","tid":1263362,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T22:30:35.000Z","msg":"健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1be12aa856e010aa779829f36735bc64688e6e7","tid":1263362,"uid":34616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T22:40:43.000Z","msg":"祝伯伯身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}